{
  "video_id": "bVV2Zk88beY",
  "title": "I grew up in the Westboro Baptist Church. Here's why I left | Megan Phelps-Roper",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12780.0,
      "end_time": 15436.0,
      "text": "I was a blue-eyed, chubby-cheeked five-year-old"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15460.0,
      "end_time": 18580.0,
      "text": "when I joined my family on the picket line for the first time."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19660.0,
      "end_time": 21780.0,
      "text": "My mom made me leave my dolls in the minivan."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22620.0,
      "end_time": 25716.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d stand on a street corner in the heavy Kansas humidity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25740.0,
      "end_time": 28355.0,
      "text": "surrounded by a few dozen relatives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28380.0,
      "end_time": 31500.0,
      "text": "with my tiny fists clutching a sign that I couldn&#39;t read yet:"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32500.0,
      "end_time": 34100.0,
      "text": "\"Gays are worthy of death.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34940.0,
      "end_time": 36140.0,
      "text": "This was the beginning."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36860.0,
      "end_time": 39760.0,
      "text": "Our protests soon became a daily occurrence"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39100.0,
      "end_time": 41360.0,
      "text": "and an international phenomenon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41600.0,
      "end_time": 43516.0,
      "text": "and as a member of Westboro Baptist Church,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43540.0,
      "end_time": 46676.0,
      "text": "I became a fixture on picket lines across the country."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 46700.0,
      "end_time": 49360.0,
      "text": "The end of my antigay picketing career"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 49600.0,
      "end_time": 50476.0,
      "text": "and life as I knew it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 50500.0,
      "end_time": 52156.0,
      "text": "came 20 years later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 52180.0,
      "end_time": 54676.0,
      "text": "triggered in part by strangers on Twitter"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 54700.0,
      "end_time": 57380.0,
      "text": "who showed me the power of engaging the other."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 59100.0,
      "end_time": 60316.0,
      "text": "In my home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 60340.0,
      "end_time": 63460.0,
      "text": "life was framed as an epic spiritual battle between good and evil."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 64190.0,
      "end_time": 66595.0,
      "text": "The good was my church and its members,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 66620.0,
      "end_time": 68540.0,
      "text": "and the evil was everyone else."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 69700.0,
      "end_time": 71156.0,
      "text": "My church&#39;s antics were such"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 71180.0,
      "end_time": 73596.0,
      "text": "that we were constantly at odds with the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 73620.0,
      "end_time": 76419.0,
      "text": "and that reinforced our otherness on a daily basis."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 77460.0,
      "end_time": 80760.0,
      "text": "\"Make a difference between the unclean and the clean,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 80100.0,
      "end_time": 81436.0,
      "text": "the verse says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 81460.0,
      "end_time": 82795.0,
      "text": "and so we did."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 82820.0,
      "end_time": 84955.0,
      "text": "From baseball games to military funerals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 84980.0,
      "end_time": 88756.0,
      "text": "we trekked across the country with neon protest signs in hand"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 88780.0,
      "end_time": 91756.0,
      "text": "to tell others exactly how \"unclean\" they were"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 91780.0,
      "end_time": 94500.0,
      "text": "and exactly why they were headed for damnation."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 95260.0,
      "end_time": 97620.0,
      "text": "This was the focus of our whole lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 98220.0,
      "end_time": 102340.0,
      "text": "This was the only way for me to do good in a world that sits in Satan&#39;s lap."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 103180.0,
      "end_time": 105156.0,
      "text": "And like the rest of my 10 siblings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 105180.0,
      "end_time": 107636.0,
      "text": "I believed what I was taught with all my heart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 107660.0,
      "end_time": 110500.0,
      "text": "and I pursued Westboro&#39;s agenda with a special sort of zeal."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 111820.0,
      "end_time": 114740.0,
      "text": "In 2009, that zeal brought me to Twitter."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 115380.0,
      "end_time": 117795.0,
      "text": "Initially, the people I encountered on the platform"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 117820.0,
      "end_time": 120350.0,
      "text": "were just as hostile as I expected."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 120600.0,
      "end_time": 122556.0,
      "text": "They were the digital version of the screaming hordes"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 122580.0,
      "end_time": 125236.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d been seeing at protests since I was a kid."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 125260.0,
      "end_time": 127716.0,
      "text": "But in the midst of that digital brawl,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 127740.0,
      "end_time": 130760.0,
      "text": "a strange pattern developed."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 130100.0,
      "end_time": 134756.0,
      "text": "Someone would arrive at my profile with the usual rage and scorn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 134780.0,
      "end_time": 138916.0,
      "text": "I would respond with a custom mix of Bible verses, pop culture references"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 138940.0,
      "end_time": 140140.0,
      "text": "and smiley faces."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 141299.0,
      "end_time": 145436.0,
      "text": "They would be understandably confused and caught off guard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 145460.0,
      "end_time": 147340.0,
      "text": "but then a conversation would ensue."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 147940.0,
      "end_time": 149196.0,
      "text": "And it was civil --"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 149220.0,
      "end_time": 151540.0,
      "text": "full of genuine curiosity on both sides."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 152180.0,
      "end_time": 155940.0,
      "text": "How had the other come to such outrageous conclusions about the world?"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 156940.0,
      "end_time": 159420.0,
      "text": "Sometimes the conversation even bled into real life."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 159980.0,
      "end_time": 161636.0,
      "text": "People I&#39;d sparred with on Twitter"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 161660.0,
      "end_time": 163996.0,
      "text": "would come out to the picket line to see me"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 164200.0,
      "end_time": 165500.0,
      "text": "when I protested in their city."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 166660.0,
      "end_time": 168700.0,
      "text": "A man named David was one such person."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 169340.0,
      "end_time": 171780.0,
      "text": "He ran a blog called \"Jewlicious,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 172620.0,
      "end_time": 175716.0,
      "text": "and after several months of heated but friendly arguments online,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 175740.0,
      "end_time": 178140.0,
      "text": "he came out to see me at a picket in New Orleans."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 178740.0,
      "end_time": 182396.0,
      "text": "He brought me a Middle Eastern dessert from Jerusalem, where he lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 182420.0,
      "end_time": 184676.0,
      "text": "and I brought him kosher chocolate"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 184700.0,
      "end_time": 186756.0,
      "text": "and held a \"God hates Jews\" sign."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 186780.0,
      "end_time": 188836.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 188860.0,
      "end_time": 190916.0,
      "text": "There was no confusion about our positions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 190940.0,
      "end_time": 194100.0,
      "text": "but the line between friend and foe was becoming blurred."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 194620.0,
      "end_time": 196876.0,
      "text": "We&#39;d started to see each other as human beings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 196900.0,
      "end_time": 199100.0,
      "text": "and it changed the way we spoke to one another."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 200100.0,
      "end_time": 201316.0,
      "text": "It took time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 201340.0,
      "end_time": 204380.0,
      "text": "but eventually these conversations planted seeds of doubt in me."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 204900.0,
      "end_time": 208556.0,
      "text": "My friends on Twitter took the time to understand Westboro&#39;s doctrines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 208580.0,
      "end_time": 209796.0,
      "text": "and in doing so,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 209820.0,
      "end_time": 213190.0,
      "text": "they were able to find inconsistencies I&#39;d missed my entire life."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 213940.0,
      "end_time": 216835.0,
      "text": "Why did we advocate the death penalty for gays"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 216860.0,
      "end_time": 220420.0,
      "text": "when Jesus said, \"Let he who is without sin cast the first stone?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 221100.0,
      "end_time": 223555.0,
      "text": "How could we claim to love our neighbor"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 223580.0,
      "end_time": 226180.0,
      "text": "while at the same time praying for God to destroy them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 227700.0,
      "end_time": 231516.0,
      "text": "The truth is that the care shown to me by these strangers on the internet"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 231540.0,
      "end_time": 233260.0,
      "text": "was itself a contradiction."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 234200.0,
      "end_time": 235276.0,
      "text": "It was growing evidence"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 235300.0,
      "end_time": 238780.0,
      "text": "that people on the other side were not the demons I&#39;d been led to believe."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 240200.0,
      "end_time": 242200.0,
      "text": "These realizations were life-altering."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 243600.0,
      "end_time": 246316.0,
      "text": "Once I saw that we were not the ultimate arbiters of divine truth"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 246340.0,
      "end_time": 248116.0,
      "text": "but flawed human beings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 248140.0,
      "end_time": 249700.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t pretend otherwise."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 250260.0,
      "end_time": 252715.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t justify our actions --"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 252740.0,
      "end_time": 255716.0,
      "text": "especially our cruel practice of protesting funerals"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 255740.0,
      "end_time": 257420.0,
      "text": "and celebrating human tragedy."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 259339.0,
      "end_time": 260796.0,
      "text": "These shifts in my perspective"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 260820.0,
      "end_time": 263916.0,
      "text": "contributed to a larger erosion of trust in my church,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 263940.0,
      "end_time": 266900.0,
      "text": "and eventually it made it impossible for me to stay."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 268500.0,
      "end_time": 272779.0,
      "text": "In spite of overwhelming grief and terror, I left Westboro in 2012."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 274580.0,
      "end_time": 276476.0,
      "text": "In those days just after I left,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 276500.0,
      "end_time": 279500.0,
      "text": "the instinct to hide was almost paralyzing."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 280600.0,
      "end_time": 282396.0,
      "text": "I wanted to hide from the judgement of my family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 282420.0,
      "end_time": 284636.0,
      "text": "who I knew would never speak to me again --"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 284660.0,
      "end_time": 287580.0,
      "text": "people whose thoughts and opinions had meant everything to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 288100.0,
      "end_time": 291476.0,
      "text": "And I wanted to hide from the world I&#39;d rejected for so long --"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 291500.0,
      "end_time": 294236.0,
      "text": "people who had no reason at all to give me a second chance"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 294260.0,
      "end_time": 296219.0,
      "text": "after a lifetime of antagonism."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 297420.0,
      "end_time": 298996.0,
      "text": "And yet, unbelievably,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 299200.0,
      "end_time": 300476.0,
      "text": "they did."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 300500.0,
      "end_time": 303876.0,
      "text": "The world had access to my past because it was all over the internet --"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 303900.0,
      "end_time": 306275.0,
      "text": "thousands of tweets and hundreds of interviews,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 306300.0,
      "end_time": 309796.0,
      "text": "everything from local TV news to \"The Howard Stern Show\" --"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 309820.0,
      "end_time": 312420.0,
      "text": "but so many embraced me with open arms anyway."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 313620.0,
      "end_time": 315716.0,
      "text": "I wrote an apology for the harm I&#39;d caused,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 315740.0,
      "end_time": 319180.0,
      "text": "but I also knew that an apology could never undo any of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 319780.0,
      "end_time": 322350.0,
      "text": "All I could do was try to build a new life"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 322600.0,
      "end_time": 325460.0,
      "text": "and find a way somehow to repair some of the damage."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 326380.0,
      "end_time": 328756.0,
      "text": "People had every reason to doubt my sincerity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 328780.0,
      "end_time": 330200.0,
      "text": "but most of them didn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 330700.0,
      "end_time": 331900.0,
      "text": "And --"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 332500.0,
      "end_time": 333716.0,
      "text": "given my history,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 333740.0,
      "end_time": 335676.0,
      "text": "it was more than I could&#39;ve hoped for --"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 335700.0,
      "end_time": 338156.0,
      "text": "forgiveness and the benefit of the doubt."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 338180.0,
      "end_time": 339420.0,
      "text": "It still amazes me."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 340340.0,
      "end_time": 342900.0,
      "text": "I spent my first year away from home"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 344300.0,
      "end_time": 345996.0,
      "text": "adrift with my younger sister,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 346200.0,
      "end_time": 347580.0,
      "text": "who had chosen to leave with me."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 348620.0,
      "end_time": 350156.0,
      "text": "We walked into an abyss,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 350180.0,
      "end_time": 353876.0,
      "text": "but we were shocked to find the light and a way forward"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 353900.0,
      "end_time": 356500.0,
      "text": "in the same communities we&#39;d targeted for so long."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 357420.0,
      "end_time": 358636.0,
      "text": "David,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 358660.0,
      "end_time": 360556.0,
      "text": "my \"Jewlicious\" friend from Twitter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 360580.0,
      "end_time": 364316.0,
      "text": "invited us to spend time among a Jewish community in Los Angeles."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 364340.0,
      "end_time": 367556.0,
      "text": "We slept on couches in the home of a Hasidic rabbi and his wife"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 367580.0,
      "end_time": 368780.0,
      "text": "and their four kids --"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 369420.0,
      "end_time": 372236.0,
      "text": "the same rabbi that I&#39;d protested three years earlier"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 372260.0,
      "end_time": 374460.0,
      "text": "with a sign that said, \"Your rabbi is a whore.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 376740.0,
      "end_time": 380676.0,
      "text": "We spent long hours talking about theology and Judaism and life"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 380700.0,
      "end_time": 382916.0,
      "text": "while we washed dishes in their kosher kitchen"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 382940.0,
      "end_time": 384660.0,
      "text": "and chopped vegetables for dinner."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 385420.0,
      "end_time": 386980.0,
      "text": "They treated us like family."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 387460.0,
      "end_time": 389556.0,
      "text": "They held nothing against us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 389580.0,
      "end_time": 391419.0,
      "text": "and again I was astonished."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 392580.0,
      "end_time": 394276.0,
      "text": "That period was full of turmoil,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 394300.0,
      "end_time": 396596.0,
      "text": "but one part I&#39;ve returned to often"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 396620.0,
      "end_time": 399500.0,
      "text": "is a surprising realization I had during that time --"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 400340.0,
      "end_time": 404596.0,
      "text": "that it was a relief and a privilege to let go of the harsh judgments"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 404620.0,
      "end_time": 408540.0,
      "text": "that instinctively ran through my mind about nearly every person I saw."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 409500.0,
      "end_time": 412220.0,
      "text": "I realized that now I needed to learn."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 412860.0,
      "end_time": 414100.0,
      "text": "I needed to listen."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 415340.0,
      "end_time": 417476.0,
      "text": "This has been at the front of my mind lately,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 417500.0,
      "end_time": 420436.0,
      "text": "because I can&#39;t help but see in our public discourse"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 420460.0,
      "end_time": 424460.0,
      "text": "so many of the same destructive impulses that ruled my former church."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 425380.0,
      "end_time": 429316.0,
      "text": "We celebrate tolerance and diversity more than at any other time in memory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 429340.0,
      "end_time": 431580.0,
      "text": "and still we grow more and more divided."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 432260.0,
      "end_time": 434156.0,
      "text": "We want good things --"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 434180.0,
      "end_time": 437796.0,
      "text": "justice, equality, freedom, dignity, prosperity --"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 437820.0,
      "end_time": 439116.0,
      "text": "but the path we&#39;ve chosen"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 439140.0,
      "end_time": 442260.0,
      "text": "looks so much like the one I walked away from four years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 443180.0,
      "end_time": 446316.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve broken the world into us and them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 446340.0,
      "end_time": 448395.0,
      "text": "only emerging from our bunkers long enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 448420.0,
      "end_time": 450660.0,
      "text": "to lob rhetorical grenades at the other camp."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 451660.0,
      "end_time": 455356.0,
      "text": "We write off half the country as out-of-touch liberal elites"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 455380.0,
      "end_time": 457540.0,
      "text": "or racist misogynist bullies."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 458200.0,
      "end_time": 461419.0,
      "text": "No nuance, no complexity, no humanity."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 462300.0,
      "end_time": 466116.0,
      "text": "Even when someone does call for empathy and understanding for the other side,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 466140.0,
      "end_time": 468360.0,
      "text": "the conversation nearly always devolves"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 468600.0,
      "end_time": 470300.0,
      "text": "into a debate about who deserves more empathy."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 471540.0,
      "end_time": 473360.0,
      "text": "And just as I learned to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 473600.0,
      "end_time": 476596.0,
      "text": "we routinely refuse to acknowledge the flaws in our positions"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 476620.0,
      "end_time": 478260.0,
      "text": "or the merits in our opponent&#39;s."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 479200.0,
      "end_time": 480820.0,
      "text": "Compromise is anathema."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 481420.0,
      "end_time": 485540.0,
      "text": "We even target people on our own side when they dare to question the party line."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 486620.0,
      "end_time": 491116.0,
      "text": "This path has brought us cruel, sniping, deepening polarization,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 491140.0,
      "end_time": 492740.0,
      "text": "and even outbreaks of violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 493380.0,
      "end_time": 495436.0,
      "text": "I remember this path."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 495460.0,
      "end_time": 497620.0,
      "text": "It will not take us where we want to go."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 498900.0,
      "end_time": 501620.0,
      "text": "What gives me hope is that we can do something about this."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 502380.0,
      "end_time": 504200.0,
      "text": "The good news is that it&#39;s simple,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 504660.0,
      "end_time": 506420.0,
      "text": "and the bad news is that it&#39;s hard."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 507200.0,
      "end_time": 510979.0,
      "text": "We have to talk and listen to people we disagree with."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 511860.0,
      "end_time": 513756.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s hard because we often can&#39;t fathom"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 513780.0,
      "end_time": 515819.0,
      "text": "how the other side came to their positions."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 516620.0,
      "end_time": 519196.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s hard because righteous indignation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 519220.0,
      "end_time": 522396.0,
      "text": "that sense of certainty that ours is the right side,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 522419.0,
      "end_time": 523978.0,
      "text": "is so seductive."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 524739.0,
      "end_time": 528760.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s hard because it means extending empathy and compassion"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 528100.0,
      "end_time": 530619.0,
      "text": "to people who show us hostility and contempt."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 531420.0,
      "end_time": 534378.0,
      "text": "The impulse to respond in kind is so tempting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 535180.0,
      "end_time": 537116.0,
      "text": "but that isn&#39;t who we want to be."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 537140.0,
      "end_time": 538795.0,
      "text": "We can resist."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 538820.0,
      "end_time": 543276.0,
      "text": "And I will always be inspired to do so by those people I encountered on Twitter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 543300.0,
      "end_time": 546996.0,
      "text": "apparent enemies who became my beloved friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 547200.0,
      "end_time": 550436.0,
      "text": "And in the case of one particularly understanding and generous guy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 550460.0,
      "end_time": 551660.0,
      "text": "my husband."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 552620.0,
      "end_time": 555460.0,
      "text": "There was nothing special about the way I responded to him."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 556780.0,
      "end_time": 559200.0,
      "text": "What was special was their approach."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 559900.0,
      "end_time": 562476.0,
      "text": "I thought about it a lot over the past few years"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 562500.0,
      "end_time": 565356.0,
      "text": "and I found four things they did differently"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 565380.0,
      "end_time": 567460.0,
      "text": "that made real conversation possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 568820.0,
      "end_time": 571156.0,
      "text": "These four steps were small but powerful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 571180.0,
      "end_time": 574939.0,
      "text": "and I do everything I can to employ them in difficult conversations today."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 576600.0,
      "end_time": 579260.0,
      "text": "The first is don&#39;t assume bad intent."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 580600.0,
      "end_time": 581516.0,
      "text": "My friends on Twitter realized"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 581540.0,
      "end_time": 584476.0,
      "text": "that even when my words were aggressive and offensive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 584500.0,
      "end_time": 587396.0,
      "text": "I sincerely believed I was doing the right thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 587420.0,
      "end_time": 590396.0,
      "text": "Assuming ill motives almost instantly cuts us off"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 590420.0,
      "end_time": 594716.0,
      "text": "from truly understanding why someone does and believes as they do."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 594740.0,
      "end_time": 596476.0,
      "text": "We forget that they&#39;re a human being"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 596500.0,
      "end_time": 599476.0,
      "text": "with a lifetime of experience that shaped their mind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 599500.0,
      "end_time": 602196.0,
      "text": "and we get stuck on that first wave of anger,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 602220.0,
      "end_time": 605820.0,
      "text": "and the conversation has a very hard time ever moving beyond it."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 606620.0,
      "end_time": 609276.0,
      "text": "But when we assume good or neutral intent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 609300.0,
      "end_time": 612300.0,
      "text": "we give our minds a much stronger framework for dialogue."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 613980.0,
      "end_time": 616820.0,
      "text": "The second is ask questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 617580.0,
      "end_time": 620156.0,
      "text": "When we engage people across ideological divides,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 620180.0,
      "end_time": 622636.0,
      "text": "asking questions helps us map the disconnect"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 622660.0,
      "end_time": 624459.0,
      "text": "between our differing points of view."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 625200.0,
      "end_time": 627915.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s important because we can&#39;t present effective arguments"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 627940.0,
      "end_time": 631300.0,
      "text": "if we don&#39;t understand where the other side is actually coming from"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 632140.0,
      "end_time": 636260.0,
      "text": "and because it gives them an opportunity to point out flaws in our positions."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 636900.0,
      "end_time": 639356.0,
      "text": "But asking questions serves another purpose;"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 639380.0,
      "end_time": 641860.0,
      "text": "it signals to someone that they&#39;re being heard."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 642580.0,
      "end_time": 644716.0,
      "text": "When my friends on Twitter stopped accusing"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 644740.0,
      "end_time": 646516.0,
      "text": "and started asking questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 646540.0,
      "end_time": 648780.0,
      "text": "I almost automatically mirrored them."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 649580.0,
      "end_time": 651436.0,
      "text": "Their questions gave me room to speak,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 651460.0,
      "end_time": 654836.0,
      "text": "but they also gave me permission to ask them questions"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 654860.0,
      "end_time": 657200.0,
      "text": "and to truly hear their responses."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 657700.0,
      "end_time": 660500.0,
      "text": "It fundamentally changed the dynamic of our conversation."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 662140.0,
      "end_time": 663939.0,
      "text": "The third is stay calm."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 664820.0,
      "end_time": 666636.0,
      "text": "This takes practice and patience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 666660.0,
      "end_time": 667980.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s powerful."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 668540.0,
      "end_time": 672836.0,
      "text": "At Westboro, I learned not to care how my manner of speaking affected others."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 672860.0,
      "end_time": 675916.0,
      "text": "I thought my rightness justified my rudeness --"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 675940.0,
      "end_time": 679676.0,
      "text": "harsh tones, raised voices, insults, interruptions --"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 679700.0,
      "end_time": 682140.0,
      "text": "but that strategy is ultimately counterproductive."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 682780.0,
      "end_time": 686555.0,
      "text": "Dialing up the volume and the snark is natural in stressful situations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 686580.0,
      "end_time": 691580.0,
      "text": "but it tends to bring the conversation to an unsatisfactory, explosive end."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 692420.0,
      "end_time": 695675.0,
      "text": "When my husband was still just an anonymous Twitter acquaintance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 695700.0,
      "end_time": 698556.0,
      "text": "our discussions frequently became hard and pointed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 698580.0,
      "end_time": 700540.0,
      "text": "but we always refused to escalate."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 701180.0,
      "end_time": 703116.0,
      "text": "Instead, he would change the subject."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 703140.0,
      "end_time": 705356.0,
      "text": "He would tell a joke or recommend a book"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 705380.0,
      "end_time": 708580.0,
      "text": "or gently excuse himself from the conversation."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 709380.0,
      "end_time": 711236.0,
      "text": "We knew the discussion wasn&#39;t over,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 711260.0,
      "end_time": 714580.0,
      "text": "just paused for a time to bring us back to an even keel."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 715420.0,
      "end_time": 718596.0,
      "text": "People often lament that digital communication makes us less civil,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 718620.0,
      "end_time": 722860.0,
      "text": "but this is one advantage that online conversations have over in-person ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 723500.0,
      "end_time": 726116.0,
      "text": "We have a buffer of time and space"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 726140.0,
      "end_time": 729460.0,
      "text": "between us and the people whose ideas we find so frustrating."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 730100.0,
      "end_time": 732156.0,
      "text": "We can use that buffer."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 732180.0,
      "end_time": 735876.0,
      "text": "Instead of lashing out, we can pause, breathe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 735900.0,
      "end_time": 738760.0,
      "text": "change the subject or walk away,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 738100.0,
      "end_time": 740540.0,
      "text": "and then come back to it when we&#39;re ready."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 742200.0,
      "end_time": 743220.0,
      "text": "And finally ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 744580.0,
      "end_time": 745780.0,
      "text": "make the argument."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 747940.0,
      "end_time": 749236.0,
      "text": "This might seem obvious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 749260.0,
      "end_time": 751836.0,
      "text": "but one side effect of having strong beliefs"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 751860.0,
      "end_time": 753476.0,
      "text": "is that we sometimes assume"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 753500.0,
      "end_time": 758596.0,
      "text": "that the value of our position is or should be obvious and self-evident,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 758620.0,
      "end_time": 760836.0,
      "text": "that we shouldn&#39;t have to defend our positions"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 760860.0,
      "end_time": 763956.0,
      "text": "because they&#39;re so clearly right and good"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 763980.0,
      "end_time": 766556.0,
      "text": "that if someone doesn&#39;t get it, it&#39;s their problem --"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 766580.0,
      "end_time": 768500.0,
      "text": "that it&#39;s not my job to educate them."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 769380.0,
      "end_time": 770716.0,
      "text": "But if it were that simple,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 770740.0,
      "end_time": 772540.0,
      "text": "we would all see things the same way."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 773180.0,
      "end_time": 775636.0,
      "text": "As kind as my friends on Twitter were,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 775660.0,
      "end_time": 778360.0,
      "text": "if they hadn&#39;t actually made their arguments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 778600.0,
      "end_time": 781619.0,
      "text": "it would&#39;ve been so much harder for me to see the world in a different way."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 782780.0,
      "end_time": 785196.0,
      "text": "We are all a product of our upbringing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 785220.0,
      "end_time": 787740.0,
      "text": "and our beliefs reflect our experiences."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 788380.0,
      "end_time": 791900.0,
      "text": "We can&#39;t expect others to spontaneously change their own minds."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 792380.0,
      "end_time": 793796.0,
      "text": "If we want change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 793820.0,
      "end_time": 795540.0,
      "text": "we have to make the case for it."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 796980.0,
      "end_time": 801360.0,
      "text": "My friends on Twitter didn&#39;t abandon their beliefs or their principles --"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 801600.0,
      "end_time": 802260.0,
      "text": "only their scorn."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 803600.0,
      "end_time": 806675.0,
      "text": "They channeled their infinitely justifiable offense"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 806700.0,
      "end_time": 810820.0,
      "text": "and came to me with pointed questions tempered with kindness and humor."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 811700.0,
      "end_time": 813796.0,
      "text": "They approached me as a human being,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 813820.0,
      "end_time": 815396.0,
      "text": "and that was more transformative"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 815420.0,
      "end_time": 819660.0,
      "text": "than two full decades of outrage, disdain and violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 820580.0,
      "end_time": 824356.0,
      "text": "I know that some might not have the time or the energy or the patience"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 824380.0,
      "end_time": 825636.0,
      "text": "for extensive engagement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 825660.0,
      "end_time": 827716.0,
      "text": "but as difficult as it can be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 827740.0,
      "end_time": 830236.0,
      "text": "reaching out to someone we disagree with"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 830260.0,
      "end_time": 832540.0,
      "text": "is an option that is available to all of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 833100.0,
      "end_time": 836916.0,
      "text": "And I sincerely believe that we can do hard things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 836940.0,
      "end_time": 839580.0,
      "text": "not just for them but for us and our future."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 840300.0,
      "end_time": 842795.0,
      "text": "Escalating disgust and intractable conflict"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 842820.0,
      "end_time": 844956.0,
      "text": "are not what we want for ourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 844980.0,
      "end_time": 846236.0,
      "text": "or our country"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 846260.0,
      "end_time": 847460.0,
      "text": "or our next generation."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 849340.0,
      "end_time": 853636.0,
      "text": "My mom said something to me a few weeks before I left Westboro,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 853660.0,
      "end_time": 855760.0,
      "text": "when I was desperately hoping"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 855100.0,
      "end_time": 857180.0,
      "text": "there was a way I could stay with my family."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 858740.0,
      "end_time": 861116.0,
      "text": "People I have loved with every pulse of my heart"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 861140.0,
      "end_time": 864476.0,
      "text": "since even before I was that chubby-cheeked five-year-old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 864500.0,
      "end_time": 867180.0,
      "text": "standing on a picket line holding a sign I couldn&#39;t read."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 867980.0,
      "end_time": 870636.0,
      "text": "She said, \"You&#39;re just a human being,"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 870660.0,
      "end_time": 872339.0,
      "text": "my dear, sweet child.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 873580.0,
      "end_time": 875836.0,
      "text": "She was asking me to be humble --"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 875860.0,
      "end_time": 878980.0,
      "text": "not to question but to trust God and my elders."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 879780.0,
      "end_time": 883315.0,
      "text": "But to me, she was missing the bigger picture --"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 883340.0,
      "end_time": 885300.0,
      "text": "that we&#39;re all just human beings."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 885940.0,
      "end_time": 888876.0,
      "text": "That we should be guided by that most basic fact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 888900.0,
      "end_time": 892116.0,
      "text": "and approach one another with generosity and compassion."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 892140.0,
      "end_time": 894436.0,
      "text": "Each one of us contributes to the communities"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 894460.0,
      "end_time": 897200.0,
      "text": "and the cultures and the societies that we make up."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 897820.0,
      "end_time": 902476.0,
      "text": "The end of this spiral of rage and blame begins with one person"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 902500.0,
      "end_time": 907260.0,
      "text": "who refuses to indulge these destructive, seductive impulses."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 907740.0,
      "end_time": 910756.0,
      "text": "We just have to decide that it&#39;s going to start with us."
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 910780.0,
      "end_time": 911996.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 912200.0,
      "end_time": 916329.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}